{"tid":1188109,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"維尼：決不走司法獨立的路","createTime":"2019-06-06T05:10:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T05:25:04.000Z","uid":177089,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f69229b8bf738eca543de7559f271989a5685b92","tid":1188109,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T05:10:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://trad.cn.rfi.fr/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20190217-%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E6%B1%BA%E4%B8%8D%E8%B5%B0%E5%8F%B8%E6%B3%95%E7%8D%A8%E7%AB%8B%E7%9A%84%E8%B7%AF-%E8%A6%81%E7%95%B6%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E8%A6%8F%E5%89%87%E5%BC%95%E9%A0%98%E8%80%85\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftrad.cn.rfi.fr%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%2F20190217-%25E7%25BF%2592%25E8%25BF%2591%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E6%25B1%25BA%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%25B5%25B0%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%25B3%2595%25E7%258D%25A8%25E7%25AB%258B%25E7%259A%2584%25E8%25B7%25AF-%25E8%25A6%2581%25E7%2595%25B6%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E8%25A6%258F%25E5%2589%2587%25E5%25BC%2595%25E9%25A0%2598%25E8%2580%2585&d=M59wMjr1KB2wSFKn0iQ%2BgqS5T01Y9%2BWuDWMC0%2BQyx7Y%3D&h=3ac2c03b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://trad.cn.rfi.fr/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20190217-%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E6%B1%BA%E4%B8%8D%E8%B5%B0%E5%8F%B8%E6%B3%95%E7%8D%A8%E7%AB%8B%E7%9A%84%E8%B7%AF-%E8%A6%81%E7%95%B6%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E8%A6%8F%E5%89%87%E5%BC%95%E9%A0%98%E8%80%85</a><br />\n<br />\n中共總書記習近平在中央全面依法治國委員會首次會議上指出，必須<span style=\"color: red;\">堅持加強黨對依法治國的領導</span>，決不能照搬別國模式和做法，<span style=\"color: red;\">決不能走司法獨立的路</span>；而在「對外鬥爭」中，中國要以法律為武器，以法治之名向攪局者說不，並積极參與國際規則的制定，「做全球治理變革進程的參與者、推動者、引領者。」<br />\n<br />\n中國事務學者林和立向本台表示，習近平的依法治國其實是<span style=\"color: red;\">黨中央說了算的法</span>，是法治的倒退。而為了挽救習近平在國內的強勢，官媒遂在中國於中美經貿戰處處退讓的情況下刊登習的講話，儘管當中包括「不走司法獨立的路」這種被視為違背西方主流價值的說話，甚或說出儼如向西方叫板的要當國際規則制定引領者的說話。<br />\n<br />\n他指出，要做到自十八大以來提出的依法治國新理念，首先是要堅持加強黨對依法治國的領導，必須堅持「<span style=\"color: red;\">黨領導立法&hellip;&hellip;，健全黨領導全面依法治國的制度和工作機制</span>」；推進時，更須堅持走中國特色的社會主義法治道路，「要從中國國情和實際出發，&hellip;&hellip;決不能照搬別國模式和做法，<span style=\"color: red;\">決不能走西方『憲政』、『三權鼎立』、『司法獨立』的路子</span>。」習近平多次公開否定憲政和三權分立，但直接否定司法獨立則屬罕見。<br />\n<br />\n滅共之父習維尼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21783711a7dcf89a1ed71438b533ef87be0a7585","tid":1188109,"uid":244186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T06:35:44.000Z","msg":"屌 宜家擺明玩曬野咁 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7d748fa3704cc8ec667dd8e7950ffd421eb0551","tid":1188109,"uid":155095,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T06:40:07.000Z","msg":"皇帝係集立法權，行政權，司法權於一身 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"616f3e968d1e8d4ffccfca695b518df304b116ab","tid":1188109,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T06:59:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab98ecf736518e0de49af2c0b35ed3bb28f1a9f3","tid":1188109,"uid":79145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T07:32:20.000Z","msg":"維尼：I&rsquo;m the king of the world"},{"pid":"3cadcd318a256820d90c59542075ebe15d8e6b08","tid":1188109,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab98ecf736518e0de49af2c0b35ed3bb28f1a9f3","tid":1188109,"uid":79145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T07:32:20.000Z","msg":"維尼：I&rsquo;m the king of the world"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T08:00:28.000Z","msg":"of  course<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2632406/org/f56296896bb9777f5f00ae88a20abfe8.jpg/Xq1sd6D2pRWDvuiPO5FTZmJ7UQSikefxjZiAB42YgAc?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2632406%2Forg%2Ff56296896bb9777f5f00ae88a20abfe8.jpg%2FXq1sd6D2pRWDvuiPO5FTZmJ7UQSikefxjZiAB42YgAc%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=c5b8b830&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"79ba98a70ece8b6aace095a546091469913468c3","tid":1